eo-namespace.yaml

Creates a Namespace for the ElasticSearch Operator. 


clo-namespace.yaml 

Creates a Namespace for the Cluster Logging Operator. 


eo-og.yaml 

Creates an Operator Group for the ElasticSearch Operator. 


eo-csc.yaml

Creates a CatalogSource to enable the ElasticSearch Operator. 


get-channel.sh

Script when run gets the channel value required for creating the subscription object. 


eo-sub.yaml 

Can be used as reference to create a subscription object. Requires the channel value modifed. 


eo-rbac.yaml 

Creates RBAC to grant Prometheus permission to access openshift-operators-redhat namespace.


cluster-logging.yaml

Reference for updating the custom resource definition for Cluster Logging. Modification to storage and resource paramaters to be changed on a per cluster basis. 


default-fluentd-ds.yaml 

Reference of the original fluentd daemon set before modification. 


fluentd-ds.yaml

Reference for updating the fluendt daemon set for logging application and system logs to an external ElasticSearch instance. 


For further details regarding OpenShift Logging (EFK) please see the deployment guide. 


